---
title: Seared Salmon & Roast Veggie Freekeh Salad With Lemon Yoghurt
description: Light, tangy and tasty is the name of this dinner’s game. For the perfect crunchy punch of texture, allow the pan to get nice and hot before you drop in the salmon, skin side down. It’s the secret to crispy skin that won’t stick!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/seared-salmon-8bc8600a.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.co.nz/recipecards/card/seared-salmon-5e3212955ccb2412b3567fcb-7c53d7f6.pdf
